ngthen america's future is the work that is being done within the four walls of the american home. children need the guiding hand of responsible parents." </p><p>... </p><p>"america is a nation of stature thanks to the great and noble men and women serving our country here and abroad. it is why we know that america will rise to face today's challenges." ... </p><p><em>to read the full op-ed, please <a href="http://www.townhall.com/columnists/mitt(candidate last)/2007/07/13/the_four_walls_of_the_american_home">click here</a>.</em></p></span>



